{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/ud9ltw","slide":7,"title":"The paper turns churn prediction into a retention playbook","textShapes":18}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/lszqtcj6","slide":7,"bbox":[72,38,34,6]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/a5gbq1or","slide":7,"text":"The paper turns churn prediction into a retention playbook","textPreview":"The paper turns churn prediction into a retention playbook","textChars":58,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,68,1020,58]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/3m94fu18","slide":7,"text":"Prediction, explanation, and action are now one pipeline instead of three disconnected outputs.","textPreview":"Prediction, explanation, and action are now one pipeline instead of three disconnected outputs.","textChars":95,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,124,900,28]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/sji5snel","slide":7,"bbox":[72,172,566,424]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/h4byhgn2","slide":7,"text":"What the paper shows","textPreview":"What the paper shows","textChars":20,"textLines":1,"bbox":[92,194,260,28]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/adsji5sn","slide":7,"bbox":[92,236,526,88]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/3ylc7u54","slide":7,"text":"1. Commitment matters most","textPreview":"1. Commitment matters most","textChars":26,"textLines":1,"bbox":[110,250,490,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/svu9knih","slide":7,"text":"Contract is the strongest SHAP driver, and month-to-month customers churn much more often than longer-term customers.","textPreview":"Contract is the strongest SHAP driver, and month-to-month customers churn much more often than longer-term customers.","textChars":117,"textLines":1,"bbox":[110,282,490,30]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/hgn29gr2","slide":7,"bbox":[92,334,526,88]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/tgfmlkjm","slide":7,"text":"2. Service quality and price pressure matter next","textPreview":"2. Service quality and price pressure matter next","textChars":49,"textLines":1,"bbox":[110,348,490,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/4vmtwra5","slide":7,"text":"OnlineSecurity, TechSupport, TotalCharges, and tenure complete the main explanation story.","textPreview":"OnlineSecurity, TechSupport, TotalCharges, and tenure complete the main explanation story.","textChars":90,"textLines":1,"bbox":[110,380,490,30]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/bat47y1k","slide":7,"bbox":[92,432,526,142]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/mp0bi9s3","slide":7,"text":"3. Themes produce action-ready personas","textPreview":"3. Themes produce action-ready personas","textChars":39,"textLines":1,"bbox":[110,446,490,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/tsvu9kni","slide":7,"text":"Theme-level SHAP clustering gives five statistically distinct groups that can be matched to retention offers.","textPreview":"Theme-level SHAP clustering gives five statistically distinct groups that can be matched to retention offers.","textChars":109,"textLines":1,"bbox":[110,478,490,84]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/47y1kre1","slide":7,"bbox":[652,172,556,424]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/bm58z25k","slide":7,"text":"How to use it next","textPreview":"How to use it next","textChars":18,"textLines":1,"bbox":[674,194,280,28]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/m1cfa9w3","slide":7,"bbox":[674,236,512,88]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/twra5gbq","slide":7,"text":"Target the largest persona first","textPreview":"Target the largest persona first","textChars":32,"textLines":1,"bbox":[692,250,476,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/4byhgn29","slide":7,"text":"The commitment-sensitive group is the biggest cluster, so contract incentives and staged retention should be the first business test.","textPreview":"The commitment-sensitive group is the biggest cluster, so contract incentives and staged retention should be the first business test.","textChars":133,"textLines":1,"bbox":[692,282,476,30]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/0je9cvix","slide":7,"bbox":[674,334,512,88]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/t47y1kre","slide":7,"text":"Then tailor the service-quality groups","textPreview":"Then tailor the service-quality groups","textChars":38,"textLines":1,"bbox":[692,348,476,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/idonyd0z","slide":7,"text":"Two separate personas point to service issues, so technical support and network improvement should be tested next.","textPreview":"Two separate personas point to service issues, so technical support and network improvement should be tested next.","textChars":114,"textLines":1,"bbox":[692,380,476,30]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/byhgn29g","slide":7,"bbox":[674,432,512,142]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/0rqd4vmt","slide":7,"text":"Extend the dataset before the next iteration","textPreview":"Extend the dataset before the next iteration","textChars":44,"textLines":1,"bbox":[692,446,476,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/tcj6tova","slide":7,"text":"More behavioral data would likely sharpen persona separation and make the action layer even more precise.","textPreview":"More behavioral data would likely sharpen persona separation and make the action layer even more precise.","textChars":105,"textLines":1,"bbox":[692,478,476,84]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/il0rqd4v","slide":7,"text":"Final message: explain the churn signal before deciding what retention action to take.","textPreview":"Final message: explain the churn signal before deciding what retention action to take.","textChars":86,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,624,1100,22]}
